{"tid":870143,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"麥記熱香餅(附圖)","createTime":"2018-10-21T01:02:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T16:32:16.000Z","uid":217716,"like":2,"dislike":19,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"0bbf5455b61a68d0561408b77c01311c10ed741a","tid":870143,"uid":217716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:02:26.000Z","msg":"有無做緊麥記既師兄解答下，麥記熱香餅而家細左？ <br />\n今日我落麥記食熱香餅，一打開，嘩，細左咁多。我諗左一陣，都係忍唔住走去問經理。<br />\n<br />\n我: 經理，唔好意思，我太耐無食麥記，想問下而家啲熱香餅改左標準，好似細左好多。<br />\n<br />\n經理: 唔係喎，我地一直都係咁大，應該係塊豬柳大左。<br />\n<br />\n我: 下，豬柳會大左？唔係掛。<br />\n<br />\n經理: 唔同批次的豬柳大小係有出入。<br />\n<br />\n聽完佢咁講，我都醒水叫佢拎份齋餅黎望下，點知都係咁細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n可能我大鄉里出城，而家新標準細左？<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/085103_673bc4d4974a0d4613b7d8908617a8bd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F085103_673bc4d4974a0d4613b7d8908617a8bd.png&h=c9461c22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/085206_7a671589d8a7a54a9e222776dc163076.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F085206_7a671589d8a7a54a9e222776dc163076.png&h=0494c5ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"12df531d3920598127d8d2ac56271dae339ed83e","tid":870143,"uid":195714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:05:50.000Z","msg":"正常兩塊並排會突少少出個盒<br />\n<br />\n利申:都係好耐無食"},{"pid":"876b8544d963b34b2f2e9ee7a55008005c947a7a","tid":870143,"uid":36478,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:10:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feb777992bd48f6d41b0931bf8b3e14ecca1f4f1","tid":870143,"uid":2795,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:10:47.000Z","msg":"係塊豬大塊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcfbd6323ba1e53ded94e3429d6f0ebc163687d0","tid":870143,"uid":217716,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"feb777992bd48f6d41b0931bf8b3e14ecca1f4f1","tid":870143,"uid":2795,"like":11,"dislike":2,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:10:47.000Z","msg":"係塊豬大塊左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:28:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/10/21/092819_0eb7fe9749970892dba31f89a6c0be59.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F10%2F21%2F092819_0eb7fe9749970892dba31f89a6c0be59.png&h=5422bd0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ed51135196ef7a3b520004b362406c5e4076219f","tid":870143,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:28:51.000Z","msg":"塊豬真係大咗"},{"pid":"8e2c8de89e51f35235d56d814aa34cc585a28a74","tid":870143,"uid":154385,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T01:54:47.000Z","msg":"其實熱香餅縮左水"},{"pid":"52b8dac1a7b536ca0f6d4f0d9499295264f3bb09","tid":870143,"uid":62062,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:03:28.000Z","msg":"其實有size 跟 為咗唔想係咁打熱香餅粉 ，但通常亂咁嚟，係咁縮水<br />\n<br />\n利伸：細個返過"},{"pid":"7cfbd25761057d92fafccc9bcfd2b289932f9436","tid":870143,"uid":197074,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"正常係要大過塊豬柳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申：現職麥記，有份煎餅"},{"pid":"d57499da96215680b423ccec1f56bd37bc09d47e","tid":870143,"uid":6290,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T02:14:06.000Z","msg":"以前個熱香餅個直徑應該有個盒咁長<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9bece5b3e621933c4cf022bb37a86a923e27eff","tid":870143,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T03:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  係個盒大咗"},{"pid":"5955c24ba9b79b16010258f6abf02c84ed1b1925","tid":870143,"uid":110656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T03:57:43.000Z","msg":"個盒細咗 環保啊"},{"pid":"01c5e11992df5bb0b55dda9cacf6642df3e5d4d9","tid":870143,"uid":134691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:28:03.000Z","msg":"塊豬柳係大左<br />\n但塊熱香餅印象中的確細塊過細個食果時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c4780a8c55a646fc0e6aee7f30847b707c433fb","tid":870143,"uid":91833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-21T16:32:16.000Z","msg":"有乜所謂，件餅難食到，加埋黃色汁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}